e bishop and threatening to take on f3 and on d4 .} 11. Be3 {White completes his development and defends the d4 -pawn.} Re8 {Occupying the open file with the Rook.} 12. h3 Bh5 ({Transposes to h3} 12... Bh5 {b3 Re8 Be3 Bf6 .}) *

